# Data Dictionary — ke2015_sleeping_beauties

## Data source
Web of Science + APS — 22M-paper citation corpus
Access: private; Provenance: Clarivate/APS licensed

## Key variables
- Unit of analysis: paper
- Time window: 1900-2013
- Sample N: 22000000
- Filter rules: citation-network construction

## Indicator definitions
- Formula: Beckendorf Bcriterion ( Beautycriterion); citation-delay + sudden-awakening metrics
- Parameters: awakening threshold
- Computation steps: build citation network, detect delayed citation burst
